"title": "5136: body",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5136",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Used in Scripture in both a physical and metaphorical sense, the body is susceptible to sin and suffering, but may be offered to God in worship and will finally be transformed by resurrection.</p>\n<h2>The body is formed by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:15-Ps139:16\">PSA 139:15–139:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">GEN 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:22\">GEN 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:8-Job10:11\">JOB 10:8–10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:5\">ECC 11:5</a></p>\n<h2>The body's appearance</h2>\n<h3>The beauty and strength of the body</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:12\">1SA 16:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:2\">1SA 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2\">2SA 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:10-Song5:16\">SNG 5:10–5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:1-Song7:9\">SNG 7:1–7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:6\">DAN 10:6</a></p>\n<h3>Clothing for the body</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:27\">EXO 22:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:42\">EXO 28:42</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:4\">LEV 16:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:30\">2KI 6:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa20:2\">ISA 20:2</a></p>\n<h2>Diseases affecting the body</h2>\n<h3>Bodily pain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:7\">JOB 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16\">GEN 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:19\">2CH 21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:5\">JOB 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:22\">JOB 14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:7\">JOB 17:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:30\">JOB 30:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:7\">PSA 38:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7\">2CO 12:7</a></p>\n<h3>Leprosy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:2-Lev13:17\">LEV 13:2–13:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:10\">NUM 12:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:29\">2SA 3:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:1-2Kgs5:2\">2KI 5:1–5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:6-2Kgs5:7\">2KI 5:6–5:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:19-2Chr26:21\">2CH 26:19–26:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:2-Matt8:3\">MAT 8:2–8:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:40-Mark1:42\">MRK 1:40–1:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:12-Luke5:13\">LUK 5:12–5:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:12-Luke17:13\">LUK 17:12–17:13</a></p>\n<h3>Boils</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:9-Exod9:11\">EXO 9:9–9:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:18-Lev13:23\">LEV 13:18–13:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:27\">DEU 28:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:35\">DEU 28:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:7\">2KI 20:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:21\">ISA 38:21</a></p>\n<h3>The marks of suffering</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:25\">JHN 20:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:27\">JHN 20:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:17\">GAL 6:17</a></p>\n<h2>Healing of the body</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:25-Mark5:29\">MRK 5:25–5:29</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:20-Matt9:22\">MAT 9:20–9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:43-Luke8:44\">LUK 8:43–8:44</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:7\">EXO 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:10\">2KI 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:14\">2KI 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:25\">JOB 33:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:3-Matt8:4\">MAT 8:3–8:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:41-Mark1:42\">MRK 1:41–1:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:13\">LUK 5:13</a></p>\n<h2>Certain actions and attitudes affect the health of the body</h2>\n<h3>The body's response to godliness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:30\">PRO 14:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:7-Prov3:8\">PRO 3:7–3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:20-Prov4:22\">PRO 4:20–4:22</a></p>\n<h3>Godliness is no guarantee of bodily health</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:23-Job21:26\">JOB 21:23–21:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:4\">PSA 73:4</a></p>\n<h3>The body's response to sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:3\">PSA 38:3</a></strong> <em>Suffering and death are the result of sin in general, but specific experiences of suffering cannot usually be traced to specific sin.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:2-Ps32:3\">PSA 32:2–32:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:4-Ps38:11\">PSA 38:4–38:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:18\">PSA 109:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:11\">PRO 5:11</a></p>\n<h3>The body's response to distress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9-Ps31:10\">PSA 31:9–31:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:25\">PSA 44:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:10\">NAM 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>The body's response to fear</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:14-Job4:15\">JOB 4:14–4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:6\">JOB 21:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:3\">ISA 21:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:15-Dan10:17\">DAN 10:15–10:17</a></p>\n<h2>Life here and now in the body</h2>\n<h3><code>In the body'' meaning</code>in this life''</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:6\">2CO 5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:8-2Cor5:10\">2CO 5:8–5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:20\">PHP 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:22\">PHP 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:24\">PHP 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:13\">2PE 1:13</a></p>\n<h3><code>Body'' meaning</code>self''</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1\">PSA 63:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:18\">GEN 47:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:37\">NEH 9:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:5\">2CO 7:5</a></p>\n<h2>Bodily relationships</h2>\n<h3>Parenthood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:4\">GEN 15:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:11\">GEN 35:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:12\">2SA 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:7\">MIC 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:19\">ROM 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:10\">HEB 7:10</a></p>\n<h3>Kinship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:1\">2SA 5:1</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:1\">1CH 11:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:23\">GEN 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:14\">GEN 29:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:2\">JDG 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:5\">NEH 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:7\">ISA 58:7</a></p>\n<h3>Marriage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:4\">1CO 7:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:5\">MAT 19:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:7-Mark10:8\">MRK 10:7–10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:28-Eph5:29\">EPH 5:28–5:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:31\">EPH 5:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:24\">GEN 2:24</a></p>\n<h2>Rituals performed on the body</h2>\n<p>Circumcision:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:13-Gen17:14\">GEN 17:13–17:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:25\">JER 9:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:11\">EPH 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:16\">LEV 15:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:7\">NUM 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:28\">LEV 19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:5\">LEV 21:5</a></p>\n<h2>The believer's body as a temple of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:19–6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:19-John2:22\">JHN 2:19–2:22</a> <em>Jesus Christ also likens his body to a temple</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:10-Rom8:11\">ROM 8:10–8:11</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are to devote their bodies to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:13\">ROM 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:13\">ROM 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:4\">1TH 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:23\">1TH 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:2\">JAS 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Sin at work in the body</h2>\n<h3>The body is subject to sinful desires</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:38\">MRK 14:38</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:6\">ROM 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:23-Rom7:24\">ROM 7:23–7:24</a></p>\n<h3>Bodily temptation is to be resisted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:12\">ROM 6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24\">ROM 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:19\">ROM 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:13-1Cor6:16\">1CO 6:13–6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:18\">1CO 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:8\">JUD 1:8</a></p>\n<h3>Undue concern for the body is to be avoided</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:8\">1TI 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:25-Matt6:32\">MAT 6:25–6:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:22-Luke12:30\">LUK 12:22–12:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:28\">MAT 10:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:4-Luke12:5\">LUK 12:4–12:5</a></p>\n<h2>The resurrection of the body</h2>\n<h3>Dead bodies restored to this life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:20-1Kgs17:22\">1KI 17:20–17:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:32-2Kgs4:36\">2KI 4:32–4:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:21\">2KI 13:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:25\">MAT 9:25</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:41-Mark5:42\">MRK 5:41–5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:54-Luke8:55\">LUK 8:54–8:55</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:14-Luke7:15\">LUK 7:14–7:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:43-John11:44\">JHN 11:43–11:44</a></p>\n<h3>The resurrection body of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:21\">PHP 3:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:9-Ps16:10\">PSA 16:9–16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:19\">ISA 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:23\">ROM 8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:35-1Cor15:54\">1CO 15:35–15:54</a></p>\n<h2>Bodies other than human</h2>\n<h3>Idols of pagan gods</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:4\">1SA 5:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:4-Ps115:7\">PSA 115:4–115:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:15-Ps135:17\">PSA 135:15–135:17</a></p>\n<h3>Angelic beings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:2\">ISA 6:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:11\">EZK 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:23\">EZK 1:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:12\">EZK 10:12</a></p>\n<h3>Heavenly bodies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:29\">MAT 24:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:25\">MRK 13:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:26\">LUK 21:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:42\">ACT 7:42</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:40-1Cor15:41\">1CO 15:40–15:41</a></p>\n<h2>Body in a metaphorical sense</h2>\n<p>A body of people:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:20\">EZR 8:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:14\">1TI 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:8\">DEU 4:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:20\">ROM 2:20</a></p>",
